{"tid":1986070,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佩雷斯主席算唔算係最屈機嘅主席？！","createTime":"2020-04-23T14:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T00:49:36.000Z","uid":38189,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6376e0bb8c690040015561e4a90f07b33f69abb8","tid":1986070,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"創造皇馬皇朝呢啲唔使多講就係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢最勁係用錢用得好啱 每部棋都計算得好完美...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用極低價錢入摩迪+卻奧斯 兩大歷史級中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高價買人又極少失敗 3000m買高圖爾斯都好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求其整件洛迪高/為你收屍 都勁過隔離巴塞件10000m丹比利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賓斯馬呢啲撚樣都可以用足十年又冇咩大問題，C朗走後用咗一年就可以重回聯賽爭冠行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩哥真係屈能到哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc77d4bebab79906ef75d19c0c2d047d8c17214","tid":1986070,"uid":35348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"毛主席"},{"pid":"dd91ae34b39601524b46fda2d7a09c1cb208a8f9","tid":1986070,"uid":47268,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"會然都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63048f7b1d4ec9cfa1114883249a8fc8a8e729e0","tid":1986070,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc77d4bebab79906ef75d19c0c2d047d8c17214","tid":1986070,"uid":35348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"毛主席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42af0d212933af98bba3080cd8d51b31bbcf5f4b","tid":1986070,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:52:3